OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting with extensive and in
OL,6,Fplaces thick fog across the east, this
OL,7,Fmost clearing by mid-morning. Then
OL,8,Fsunny, although the sunshine will be
OL,9,Foften hazy. Becoming warm for inland
OL,10,Fareas, whilst the coast remains cooler
OL,11,Fwith light onshore winds developing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely clear initially then
OL,14,Fmist and low cloud is expected to
OL,15,Fextend inland from the coast. Chance
OL,16,Fof a slight frost, and patchy fog, for
OL,17,Fany places that remain clear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
